1
00:01:24,520 --> 00:01:25,120
Jiang Li

2
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:26,160
Come here.

3
00:01:32,320 --> 00:01:32,960
Look at this.

4
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:37,120
This is...

5
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:39,840
In Shen Qing's notebook,

6
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:41,280
a Demon Idol like this appeared.

7
00:01:41,920 --> 00:01:43,080
Is there a meaning behind it?

8
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:44,800
Usually, when people worship gods,

9
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,400
it is for honorable wishes.

10
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:47,640
Worshipping ghosts,

11
00:01:47,920 --> 00:01:49,680
however, is for hidden desires.

12
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:51,720
This kind of Demon Idol

13
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:53,240
is different from other idols.

14
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:56,400
It requires human blood offerings.

15
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:02,280
It seems Cheng Hui

16
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:04,120
isn't as everyone says,

17
00:02:04,360 --> 00:02:05,640
so honest and simple.

18
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:44,000
Through Cheng Hui's lens,

19
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,720
Lisa is truly beautiful.

20
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,080
So,

21
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:56,200
this house was a dowry for Lisa?

22
00:02:56,920 --> 00:02:57,360
Yes.

23
00:02:57,480 --> 00:02:58,560
By comparison,

24
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,480
Sir's background was much poorer.

25
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:04,760
Did her parents agree to the marriage?

26
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,920
At first, they didn't agree.

27
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,640
But since Madam is their only daughter,

28
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:09,760
they eventually compromised.

29
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:13,120
Did her parents live in this villa area too?

30
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,560
After the elders gave this villa

31
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:16,000
to Sir and Madam,

32
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,240
they moved to the suburbs.

33
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,440
Do you know the address?

34
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:21,520
That, I do know.

35
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,160
But the two elders, two years ago,

36
00:03:23,160 --> 00:03:24,520
passed away one after another.

37
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:34,240
Do you know if that house has been sold?

38
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:35,800
I heard it is occupied by

39
00:03:35,800 --> 00:03:37,440
Mr. Cheng Hui's younger brother.

40
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,720
Neighbors say Madam is a jinx.

41
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:41,520
First, she brought death to her parents,

42
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:43,320
and now even Sir is gone.

43
00:03:44,920 --> 00:03:45,480
Thank you.

44
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:47,000
Sorry to bother you today.

45
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:49,160
Thanks.

46
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:52,920
The talk about being a jinx

47
00:03:52,920 --> 00:03:55,280
is just a fig leaf for the ignorant.

48
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:58,240
Perhaps someone

49
00:03:58,240 --> 00:03:59,960
wants to cover up the truth.

50
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:05,200
Since when did Cheng Hui have a brother?

51
00:04:06,360 --> 00:04:07,640
I looked into his records.

52
00:04:07,920 --> 00:04:09,840
The relatives section only listed Lisa.

53
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:12,360
In just two short years,

54
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:14,440
three people in this family have died.

55
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:15,920
There is definitely something wrong.

56
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:18,560
Didn't you just

57
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:20,160
scoff at such superstitious talk

58
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,200
a moment ago?

59
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:22,200
I don't believe it.

60
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,320
I mean to say,

61
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:24,800
where there is talk of ghosts and gods,

62
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:28,280
there must be someone playing tricks.

63
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:40,800
What do you guys want?

64
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,880
What's going on?

65
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:47,080
What's wrong, baby?

66
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:50,560
Police.

67
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:51,920
Is something wrong?

68
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,480
You're Cheng Hui's brother.

69
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:01,400
Thanks, boss.

70
00:05:01,520 --> 00:05:03,240
Babes, we'll continue tonight.

71
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:11,960
Come on, come on.

72
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,480
Police. Sit, sit.

73
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,400
When was the last time you saw Cheng Hui?

74
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:16,640
I don't remember clearly.

75
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:18,480
I go to him when I'm out of money.

76
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:21,040
You don't seem to care at all.

77
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:22,200
Did something happen to him?

78
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:23,600
What happened to him?

79
00:05:23,760 --> 00:05:25,560
He was killed last night.

80
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,720
How is that possible?

81
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:30,280
You must be sent by that bitch Lisa.

82
00:05:30,280 --> 00:05:32,040
To kick us out, right?

83
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:35,280
Seems you don't get along very well.

84
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:37,040
That woman is so stingy.

85
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,400
Every time I ask my brother for money,

86
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:40,200
I have to watch her mood.

87
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,600
She meant your relationship with your brother.

88
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:44,200
He's dead.

89
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:46,400
You don't seem sad at all.

90
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,800
You seem more concerned about the house.

91
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:50,760
Is he really dead?

92
00:05:51,840 --> 00:05:53,600
Is it because you couldn't get money,

93
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,960
that you killed Cheng Hui?

94
00:05:55,960 --> 00:05:56,640
What?

95
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,880
Are you trying to scare me?

96
00:05:58,080 --> 00:05:59,080
Last night, the whole night,

97
00:05:59,080 --> 00:06:00,680
I was with those girls.

98
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:02,280
They can vouch for me.

99
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,200
You can't leave Tuo Cheng for now.

100
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:10,520
Let's go.

101
00:06:10,520 --> 00:06:11,080
Hey, come on.

102
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:11,720
Wait.

103
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,280
You should go check on Lisa.

104
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:16,960
She jinxed her parents to death first.

105
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:18,720
And now she's jinxed my brother.

106
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:19,480
And another thing.

107
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:22,040
My brother's casino makes good money.

108
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:23,400
I'm his own brother.

109
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,440
That money should all be mine, right?

110
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,640
Who knows?

111
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:29,800
Don't go!

112
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,440
We haven't finished talking yet! What are you doing?

113
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:12,600
Chief

114
00:07:13,200 --> 00:07:14,360
Cheng Meng's alibi

115
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,400
has been verified.

116
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:16,200
It checks out.

117
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,880
No issues.

118
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:19,840
Chief.

119
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:20,640
I'm back.

120
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:22,160
I'll get some water first.

121
00:07:25,400 --> 00:07:27,160
Any news on Lisa?

122
00:07:29,600 --> 00:07:30,040
Chief.

123
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,400
Airports,

124
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:33,400
stations, small motels...

125
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:34,040
we checked them all.

126
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:35,040
Nothing.

127
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:38,800
Her husband died,

128
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:40,760
and she just vanished into thin air.

129
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:42,720
She is a suspect.

130
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:46,040
But what is her motive?

131
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:49,560
If we say Lisa

132
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:51,600
brings misfortune to people,

133
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:53,960
I think Cheng Hui is more like a jinx.

134
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:54,600
What?

135
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,800
What did you say?

136
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:00,760
I said,

137
00:08:01,960 --> 00:08:03,720
if Lisa brings misfortune to people,

138
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:06,000
I feel Cheng Hui is more like a jinx.

139
00:08:06,760 --> 00:08:09,160
What does that have to do with the motive?

140
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,120
Think about it.

141
00:08:10,400 --> 00:08:12,160
After Cheng Hui went to Lisa's home,

142
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:14,160
her family hasn't had a good day.

143
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:16,200
Not only did both parents pass away,

144
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,960
but the casino business also went downhill.

145
00:08:20,840 --> 00:08:22,040
Are you suspecting

146
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:24,080
that the misfortunes Lisa's family suffered

147
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,400
weren't accidental?

148
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:28,160
Well,

149
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:29,720
she...

150
00:08:30,080 --> 00:08:31,600
Her mother died in a car accident.

151
00:08:31,840 --> 00:08:32,520
Her father...

152
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:33,960
was bitten to death

153
00:08:34,160 --> 00:08:34,720
by a gambler.

154
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,000
I think

155
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,560
these are all unforeseeable factors.

156
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,880
Two things happening at the same time...

157
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,440
isn't impossible.

158
00:08:43,280 --> 00:08:46,360
After Cheng Hui took over Lisa's family casino,

159
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,640
he replaced all the staff.

160
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,440
Is that a coincidence too?

161
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,520
Also, Lisa's parents

162
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:54,960
repeatedly opposed Cheng Hui and Lisa being together.

163
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:59,360
If Lisa's parents' deaths

164
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,840
are really related to Cheng Hui,

165
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:04,040
then Lisa indeed has a major motive.

166
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:05,720
Jiang Li,

167
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,600
re-investigate

168
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,120
the cause of death of Lisa's parents.

169
00:09:10,160 --> 00:09:11,360
Ma Nuo, Mei Dong,

170
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,840
you continue to search for

171
00:09:13,160 --> 00:09:14,080
Lisa's whereabouts.

172
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:14,720
Yes, sir.

173
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,360
Yes, sir.

174
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,320
Let's go.

175
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:28,760
Found it.

176
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:31,080
This is the record of the car accident.

177
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,080
Thank you.

178
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:52,440
Cheng Hui was driving during the accident?

179
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,040
Yes.

180
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,680
But he only suffered minor injuries.

181
00:09:57,400 --> 00:09:59,080
We investigated the scene,

182
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:00,200
and didn't find any issues.

183
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,200
Besides,

184
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:02,520
over at Shenshuiwan West Road,

185
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:03,600
there is a T-junction.

186
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,000
The entrance is a downhill slope.

187
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,600
The view is easily obstructed.

188
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,520
Vehicle scrapes are common there.

189
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,880
Can I take a photo?

190
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:11,920
Of course.

191
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:16,320
I'm sorry, sir.

192
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:18,000
No info on the person you're looking for.

193
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:20,080
Alright.

194
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:21,800
Thanks.

195
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:22,800
You're welcome.

196
00:10:29,800 --> 00:10:30,920
Sitting in the back,

197
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:34,000
Lisa's mother died on the spot.

198
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:36,480
Lisa in the passenger seat and her father

199
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,760
also suffered very serious injuries.

200
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,000
But why did

201
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:41,000
only Cheng Hui suffer minor injuries?

202
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:43,760
Look.

203
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,760
Except for the injury on his forehead,

204
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:49,120
the ones on his legs and arms

205
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,560
couldn't have been caused by a car accident.

206
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,720
Are you saying...

207
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:13,960
Have some water.

208
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,840
Our Lisa...

209
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,960
...has been pampered since childhood.

210
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,320
How did she ever fall for you?

211
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:32,440
But I really have to admire you.

212
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:35,240
To turn financial dependence...

213
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,960
...into an emotional investment.

214
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,440
That counts as your wisdom, I suppose.

215
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:40,840
Dad.

216
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:01,800
Watch out.

217
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:30,720
Cheng Hui staged the car accident scene on purpose.

218
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:32,040
Right.

219
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,800
Otherwise, I can't imagine...

220
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:36,400
...how he got that injury.

221
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:37,880
In that case...

222
00:12:38,120 --> 00:12:40,240
...Lisa would have a motive to kill Cheng Hui.

223
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:41,960
But I can't figure out...

224
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:44,360
...why Cheng Hui would stage a car accident.

225
00:12:44,720 --> 00:12:46,000
He clearly loves Lisa so much.

226
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,720
You just graduated from school.

227
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:50,840
There are many things...

228
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,440
...you're not particularly clear about yet.

229
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:54,360
Sometimes...

230
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:55,720
...love...

231
00:12:56,000 --> 00:12:57,480
...can be acted out.

232
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:58,840
Think about it.

233
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,480
Lisa's parents passed away.

234
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:04,040
The biggest beneficiary...

235
00:13:04,040 --> 00:13:05,440
...isn't it Cheng Hui?

236
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:08,120
That's what I find strange, too.

237
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:10,000
Ma Nuo checked.

238
00:13:10,360 --> 00:13:12,960
The properties under Lisa's parents' names...

239
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,720
...savings, and the casino...

240
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,480
...are all in Lisa's name.

241
00:13:17,840 --> 00:13:19,360
After Cheng Hui took over the casino...

242
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:21,080
...he replaced everyone with new staff.

243
00:13:22,080 --> 00:13:23,840
I just feel something isn't right about this.

244
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:27,120
If we can find the foreman from back then...

245
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:29,360
...maybe we can ask for some clues.

246
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,440
I have a way.

247
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:45,840
So...

248
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,840
...what exactly does Old Jin do?

249
00:13:50,080 --> 00:13:50,960
Him?

250
00:13:51,560 --> 00:13:53,720
He's been on these streets since he was sixteen.

251
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,520
He does whatever makes money.

252
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:58,720
Come, come.

253
00:13:59,000 --> 00:13:59,520
Come.

254
00:13:59,880 --> 00:14:01,200
Let me give a brief introduction.

255
00:14:01,680 --> 00:14:02,200
This...

256
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:04,080
...is the former foreman of Golden Elephant Casino.

257
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:05,080
His name is Old Qian.

258
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,680
Feel free to ask him any questions you have.

259
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,000
We're all brothers here.

260
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,240
Foreman Qian.

261
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:16,080
The original owner of Golden Elephant Casino...

262
00:14:16,080 --> 00:14:16,840
...how did he die?

263
00:14:16,840 --> 00:14:17,720
Do you know?

264
00:14:18,480 --> 00:14:19,680
The old boss's death...

265
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:23,360
...was very weird.

266
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:24,920
Although they say...

267
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:26,520
...the killer was caught...

268
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,200
...but...

269
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:28,600
...but I always felt...

270
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:30,720
...this wasn't done by a human.

271
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:35,360
Every Wednesday night, the old boss...

272
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:37,080
...would go to that place to eat noodles.

273
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:52,440
Boss.

274
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:54,560
Boss.

275
00:14:58,600 --> 00:14:59,200
Boss.

276
00:15:01,280 --> 00:15:03,400
Corpse oil for a lamp...

277
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:12,560
...human skin for paper...

278
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:21,240
...to write your name...

279
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:25,600
Is anyone there? Is anyone there?

280
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:27,000
...to carve my birth date...

281
00:15:27,440 --> 00:15:28,320
Open the door!

282
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,560
Let me out!

283
00:15:29,920 --> 00:15:31,720
Flesh and blood as a contract... Someone let me out!

284
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:35,320
With evil spirits as witness...

285
00:15:40,560 --> 00:15:42,440
...your death today...

286
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:46,720
...is my life.

287
00:16:20,560 --> 00:16:21,880
This way of dying sounds...

288
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:23,400
...like some kind of Occult Arts.

289
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:26,600
Then...

290
00:16:26,800 --> 00:16:28,600
...did the killer have a grudge against the old boss?

291
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:31,440
The two of them...

292
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:32,840
...didn't know each other at all.

293
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:35,080
May...

294
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:36,240
...maybe there was something...

295
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:40,720
...something controlling that person.

296
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:45,960
You started from scratch with the old boss.

297
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:46,960
Now that the casino...

298
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:48,360
...is in need of people...

299
00:16:49,040 --> 00:16:50,600
...why did you leave instead?

300
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,360
And took so many old employees with you.

301
00:16:55,600 --> 00:16:56,720
It's not that I wanted to leave.

302
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:58,840
After the old boss passed...

303
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:00,200
...this casino just...

304
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:05,600
...this casino has something unclean.

305
00:17:07,360 --> 00:17:08,080
That day...

306
00:17:08,840 --> 00:17:10,360
...I was sorting through the old boss's effects.
